Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:45.88,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hustý.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.88,0:03:47.92,Main Dialog,Sayaka's Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Sayako.
